Overview
This project takes a 100,000-row sales dataset with realistic data quality issues and transforms it into a clean, analysis-ready dataset with an interactive Excel dashboard. The goal was to replicate the workflow of a professional data analyst: identify data quality issues, document and fix them systematically, then build a dashboard that answers key business questions.
Dataset
Source: Synthetic sales transaction data (100,000 rows)
Columns: Order ID, Order Date, Customer Name, Region, Product, Category, Quantity, Unit Price, Discount %, Total Revenue, Sales Rep, Status
Files:
raw_sales_data.csv — original messy dataset
SalesPractice_100k_Clean.xlsx — final cleaned dataset + dashboard
